Woman dumped husband's body in a pit and poured concrete under Belgorod
In the Belgorod region, the woman confessed to the murder of her own husband, whom she threw into the waste pit and poured concrete, according to the website of the regional administration of the SC of the Russian Federation.
It is noted that the suspect has been living in a marriage with the deceased since 1999.
In recent years, the husband began to abuse alcohol and after another quarrel, the woman decided to kill.
"When the husband fell asleep, the suspect tied his hands and feet, put a plastic bag on his head and pressed the pillow.
When the husband stopped giving signs of life, he wrapped the body in a carpet, took it out to the yard and hid it in a dig.
The next day I called a concrete mixer and filled the pit with concrete,” the management said.
The woman later said her husband was missing.
Relatives of the deceased turned to the police, who opened the hole and recovered the body.
The investigation intends to ask the court for the arrest of the suspect.
The investigation of the criminal case is currently ongoing.
